text:

text:
Loungani Seth!
Summer19 me IME aur finance ke course sath me padhte padhte sath intern lagwa hi li thi apan ne xD
Jitna harami dikhta hai tu usse kafi acha insan hai yeh aaj bol deta hu, placement me meri sari BT sunta tha aur dilasa deta tha ki kuch nahi toh sath me lag hi jayegi apni Day-3 tak uske liye shukriya.
Jab tera call aya tha dono offer ke liye mujhe laga maze leraha bkl fir se but ab Mumbai me milenge aur is baar goa sath chalenge apan <3
Humesha khana ki jagh milne wala admi hai tu :P

text:
Breaking ne hath todne ke sath sath dil na todne wali dosti di hai tujhse! Sath me nachne se library me padhai ke naam pe sutta marne tak ka safar dekha hai. Galaxy me ladne ke bad Inter IIT me sath roye bhi hai. Goa me long drives ne yeh dosti zyada gehri kardi thi.
I never realised when you started trusting me with your secrets and I started counting on you for my fuck ups XD. You are one of the few people I can blindly trust and I know who will stick with me till the end (unless sutte se maar jau tere pehle )

PS: 304 me voh ek choreo adhuri reh gayi hai ;)
